## 🚀 Getting Started

### Quick Start Guide
1. **📥 Install Beaver**: Download and install the latest version
2. **🔑 Configure Access**: Set up GitHub Personal Access Token
3. **⚙️ Configure Settings**: Customize beaver.yml for your project
4. **🔄 Generate Wiki**: Run `beaver wiki generate owner/repo`
5. **🚀 Publish**: Optionally auto-publish to GitHub Wiki

### Command Examples
```bash
# Generate wiki locally
beaver wiki generate nyasuto/beaver --output ./wiki

# Generate and publish to GitHub Wiki
beaver wiki generate nyasuto/beaver --publish

# List existing wiki pages
beaver wiki list nyasuto/beaver

# Publish locally generated content
beaver wiki publish nyasuto/beaver
```

